brought to you by Quizilla --> got that from bev. hekhekhek seee? im not samantha haha caby has been telling me that out of all the characters from sex and the city im more samantha..not that theres anything wrong with her haha but i didnt know if it was a compliment or an insult hahaha but anyways ...blahblahblah ill finsh this later :)
You are blessed with FAERY wings. Beauty,
laughter, life, magic...that's what you are all
about. You are refreshingly innocent and happy
with your life of purity and play. Life's a
game and it's a good one. In your eyes there's
no way to lose! You can be very mischeivous and
have been known to cause trouble, but it's all
in the name of fun and not meant to really harm
anyone. You like to play tricks on people who
aren't quite as bright or clever as you - which
is almost everyone. Nature is the setting you
prefer to be in - Always. Barefoot and wild you
can't be tamed. You're probably a restless
spirit who loves to travel, and quite a
dreamer. Your creativity is astounding and your
art (of whatever media - from writing to
painting to drama) is like something from
another world - ethereal and often very
fantasy-oriented. You can either be a social
butterfly or a loner with their head in the
clouds - but rarely inbetween. You stubbornly
refuse to accept responsibility or to give in
to the wishes of others - unless you feel like
it. You have a strong passion for music and
can't imagine life without it. You'll grow up
someday, but you'll always be a child at heart.
You are adventurous and love to take risks, and
feel a deep connection with the weather,
plants, and animals. You prefer sunshine to
thunder or snow, the warmth of summer to
autumn's chill, and quiet forests to suburban
backyards. Magic through and through, you are
far more powerful than you seem, and are
capable of being extremely passionate. Though
you can be childish, naive, stubborn, and
self-absorbed, one thing is certain - life with
you will never be boring!

*~*~*Claim Your Wings - Pics and Long Answers*~*~*

im finally home. Ive nver been so eager to go home. But when i got to the airport in San Francisco i was like "mooom i dont want to gooo homeeee" haha
I played mommy when i was there and took care of my lil cousin. People prolly thought that he was my kid haha. He calls me mommy sloth and i call him baby sloth, which is kinda weird cause it sounds like (slut) haha. Id be carryin him around and hed call me mommy sloth, people mustve thought that im really messed up imagine your kid calling you mommy slut haha. BUt i thinik he got that from ice age (sloth) i dunno i fell asleep when we were watchin that movie. My lil cousin is so adorable but there are some days when i just want to strangle him or something haha cause hes really bratty. And i get pissed off cause they let him be. I mean if my kid was that bratty i would tell him off or something. And like hed sorta try to annoy you and hed sometimes say i dont want you i hate you and hed cry haha. There was this one time we were in the car, i think he woke up at the wrong side of the bed or crib haha when he hated me that day haha he was like i dont want you..dont sit beside me so i was like what do you want me to do? ill put you in the trunk so you dont have to sit beside me and he goes no! no! no! hahaha ( i like it when he says that haha) i was so pissed i wanted to cry haha he gets really annoying and i was like youre a bad boy then he goes no im not! no im not while crying. And my mom said no hes not hes a good boy im like arrrgghh i know hes a kid but okay blaaahh...hahaha

oohh! ooh! haha i saw the first guy whoever asked me out hahaha. I remember sorta promisin him before that id go out with him when i turn 16 hahahah. We watched a movie with some of his friends [sshhh...they ddnt know haha] had a blast but it was a "friendly" date. haha anyways i also earned around $60 for walkin the dog, baking cookies and wrtiting down some stuff. wooppee doo i went shoe crazy bought like 6 pairs of shoes [hahaha] i still have two back there im gona ask my dad to bring it hahaha cause we ddnt have space for mooore shoes anymore.

Im going to start goin to the gym tmrow haha. All those burgers and fries..sheessh. haha i have moreee cheecks. i hate my cheecks theyre so cheecky ahaha what am i saying.speaking of cheecks, haha 3 days before i left a huge pimple appeared on my cheeck and its sooo annoying hahah okay thats it i guess :)

Wohhoo! Im freeezin my ass off right now! hahaha Havent had a ciggie for a week now..but uhm im definitely sure i wont be quitting next year haha..as of now im going ballistic. Tons of food + cooolld weather = ciggie craving. I had like a pack with me when i left but uhmm i was really dtermined to quit so i trashed it. haha gawd..I am dying hahaha please anyone send me some haha

I havent been updating this lately. been busy with school haha "yeh right!" Went out last saturday and i had so much fun. Had dinner at chilis (*yaay* i finally saw sheyz and yeah she really is purdie and shes hella tall *envious* )and headed to racks after. I was really havin a good time. BUt when we got to racks something weird happened to me. I kept on excusing myself to go to the car and sulk alone. weird huh? I just felt off, like something was awfully wrong, felt insecure, jealous, sad and all that shit. I was in my "depressed mode". Caby and kathy followed me to the car and asked if i was okay cause i promised them id be back in 5 mintues but i didnt. I kept on going back to the car. I went back with them (cause i ddnt want kathy and caby to sulk with me in the car) then i would escape and go back to the car. haha weirdo. But, it sorta changed when i saw JOhn Arigo haha i have the biggest crush on him, well i used to. I had a couple of zombies (*yummy*) but i hardly had any space left cause we were all so full (thanks sheys! muah). I like the efffect of zombie, haha it didnt make me tipsy but it made me talkative..i should drink that more often LOL Its crazy how i get so weird..sometimes id find myself crying in front of the computer, on the bus, in the car, wherever. When i hear sappy songs, when i read something touching, when i remmber things..ho-humm im going crazy. i think i need psychiatric help! haha BUt my friend told me itll pass. i hope so. but i guess its just a phase....(to be continued hehe) anyways ive been takin all the crazy quizzes that i come across..try em! :D

School was okay. Aside from th fact that i kept on barking..haha. it was really irritating, how my throat was so itchy. I felt bad, so i went  home after attending one class. haha. I had a hard time going to school since my friends have a diffrent sched. And i miss Don. I just realized how hard this sem is going to be without him around. Its only the first week and i dont feel like going to school at all. Im quite loserish..haha yeh. I hardly hangout with any of my blockmates.  I think i have delusion of grandeur, BIGTIME! haha i always get this feeling that they dont like me or they hate me. But you cant blame me..oh welps

I just bummed around today. ate, took a shower, slept, watched Disney channel, and went online. My usual routine. Nothing exciting really happened. I got to see a lot of new faces. And i have new annoying blockmates. *yaay* haha theyre quite funny actually, so i guess theyre okay.

I chatted with some of my blockmates from last sem. And they were all wondering were Don is. So i told them that he int going to be there anymore and that hes moving to csb next year. I miss that mooofooo :/ One of my blockmates was approaching me and uhm when i looked at him he turned away haha. Guess theyre still scared of me haha. I wonder if i really look that scary..haha

My dads goin to leave for cebu tomorrow morning, and im still thinking if im going to school tomorrow. Its just the first week, so i guess we wont be doing anything much and i just hate it when the professors ask you to go in the front and introduce yourself haha. I dont like talking in front of the class. Im shy turtle, yes i am heehee :D

Im out..im gon try to get some sleep. *Cross your ftoes and fingers*, and hope that i hit my head on the wall and change my mind about not going to school :D gnyt

OH and does anybody know the title of the song that goes "Something strange is happening to me// I dont know what it is// i used to be sure, laid back and in control...blaaahh" I dont even know if i ogt the lyrics right but yeh, if you think you know the title, do inform me..thanks :D

i was alone the whole friggin day, caby was here to keep me company but she had to leave at around 5. I had to beg my brother to go home cause i was scared. I hate being alone. And during the 5 hours i spent talking to the wall, it answered back. haha BUt seriously i was contemplating on what i should do with myself. I dont know what i should do anymore. i feel helpless and hopeless most of the time. i think im starting to get tired of how things are going. I need something thats stable. Maybe i need love? *sighs* yeah i do...Me and caby just moped around in my room. And it made me sad, made me realize how lonely i am, how much i miss being in love, and how wonderful it is to love and be loved back. But theres still something that keeps me going, theres a lil hope left inside of me telling me not to give up, itll come..*Sighs* I Hope..
